{"tid":2322074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【神力女童】訓練2年舉重即變「世上最強壯」　7歲神力女童能舉起80公斤槓鈴【有片】","createTime":"2020-12-12T04:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T16:21:28.000Z","uid":271829,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"dc25cce8adddab0404af62c070330ad1e955ee16","tid":2322074,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2826077/weightlifting_thumb_20201211_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2826077%2Fweightlifting_thumb_20201211_S_600.jpg&h=c0512653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 7歲神力女童能舉起80公斤槓鈴。<br />\n<br />\n身型嬌小的7歲女童，居然舉得起80公斤的槓鈴！7歲的Rory van Ulft雖然只有120cm高，但自5歲開始練習舉重的她，訓練短短2年就能舉得起80公斤槓鈴，成為美國11歲以下和13歲以下青少年舉重比賽30公斤級的全國冠軍，是史上最年輕的冠軍。<br />\n據《每日郵報》報道，Rory van Ulft因為加拿大沒有青少年舉重比賽，所以選擇到美國參賽，結果不負眾望一舉奪冠。<br />\nRory本來是名體操運動員，每星期花9小時練體操，舉重只有4小時。只是短短訓練2年，Rory就能抓舉32公斤、挺舉42公斤、蹲舉32公斤、硬舉80公斤。<br />\n<br />\nRory表示自己很喜歡逐步變強壯的過程，因為強壯可讓她做任何事都做得更好。<br />\n&quot;我喜歡挑戰新舉重紀錄，我為自己感到驕傲。&quot;<br />\n&quot;我不會想已經發生的事和猜測將來的事，我只會清醒頭腦，然後去做。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2826077/roryvanulft_98069352_129277645426768_4190140148552392209_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2826077%2Froryvanulft_98069352_129277645426768_4190140148552392209_n_1024.jpg&h=022e726c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRory只練習了2年舉重。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2826077/roryvanulft_106104501_721471361996784_1284458337899100705_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2826077%2Froryvanulft_106104501_721471361996784_1284458337899100705_n_1024.jpg&h=a9fa1cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRory年紀小小，但頭腦聰明，專注力佳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2826077/roryvanulft_91403246_224059372281510_2362976474477047410_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2826077%2Froryvanulft_91403246_224059372281510_2362976474477047410_n_1024.jpg&h=501bbb0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRory本是體操運動員。<br />\n<br />\nRory的父母強調，Rory的安全是重中之重，訓練時有舉重教練、體操教練、運動醫學兒科醫生來指導她。而且，Rory沒有參加奧運的想法，因為實在太年輕了。Rory也指：「那些事對我完全不重要。」<br />\n不過，比起舉重其實Rory更喜歡體操。她曾在取得平衡木銅牌時告訴父母：「我更喜歡體操，因為體操不需要舉起任何東西。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XVLIOULmPtQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXVLIOULmPtQ&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=737ec35b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XVLIOULmPtQ</a>"},{"pid":"179a7598aefdf03b5312a441ddb0e0ae44e5e7c4","tid":2322074,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":23,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"應該會好矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32932b36e3b19c98a28f708b553c2dd0eb7f320","tid":2322074,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:53:15.000Z","msg":"佢應該去學埋boxing <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d085f7e421340967027b88c254050b20cdeebac2","tid":2322074,"uid":70629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:53:36.000Z","msg":"等我仲估係俄羅斯添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80961f4cd201f16baee5bd190cf69d7a28f29084","tid":2322074,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"金仔習仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398536ffbe68bfa4fa03945f6752cf13fcdc0c26","tid":2322074,"uid":171786,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"